{"id": "1187540850683691098", "channel_id": "1187304008356999169", "type": 0, "author_id": "1164258265799086080", "author_name": "metam0n", "author_bot": false, "content": "re开头的话，有两个思路。\n1.超维精通的灵感，拿到2个砍头。\n2.密契机械降神给算力。\n拿2个砍头也是有多个思路。\n1.命轮锁链随机发的。\n2.抽出来的砍头，魔术师取物。\n\n先跃迁砍到低血，再补一个砍头收割。", "timestamp": "2023-12-21T23:43:22.245000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
